Package: healthiar
Title: Quantification and monetarization of health impacts of environmental stressors
Version: 0.0.0.1
Author: Alberto Castro [aut, cre], Axel Luyten [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Alberto Castro <alberto.castrofernandez@swisstph.ch>
Description: healthiar aims to quantify and monetize health impacts of environmental stressors focusing on air pollution and noise.
